ActFederal Real Property Act
SubjectMisipawistik Cree Nation, Manitoba ** Creation **
PrecisOrder setting apart 20.235 hectares (50.00 acres) of lands, including mines and minerals for the use and benefit of the Misipawistik Cree Nation as creation of a MASIKÏSKAHK INDIAN RESERVE, located in Manitoba’s Unorganized Territory at approximately 400 kilometres from the City of Winnipeg, Manitoba.
